com.xilinx.rapidwright.edif

Class EDIFName

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.edif.EDIFName
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    EDIFLibrary, EDIFNetlist, EDIFPropertyObject

    public class EDIFName
extends java.lang.Object
    This class serves as the universal common ancestor for most all EDIF netlist objects. Primarily it serves to manage the regular name and legal EDIF rename if it exists. Created on: May 11, 2017

        protected java.lang.String updateEDIFRename()
